322
00:27:23,770 --> 00:27:24,880
Cong laughs.

323
00:27:25,260 --> 00:27:26,460
Cong jumps.

324
00:27:27,000 --> 00:27:30,040
Cong eats and sleeps.

325
00:27:30,250 --> 00:27:32,000
