341
00:28:22,270 --> 00:28:23,380
come back to me.

342
00:28:29,650 --> 00:28:31,010
I didn't lie to you, did I?

343
00:28:32,800 --> 00:28:34,280
Why was I seeing those things?

344
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:37,470
Because you have the power the Lord gave you.

345
00:28:40,310 --> 00:28:41,720
The Lord is behind a door.

346
00:28:42,960 --> 00:28:43,780
And you

347
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:45,940
are the key.

348
00:29:12,230 --> 00:29:12,780
Come.

349
00:29:24,590 --> 00:29:25,430
Cong.

350
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,110
Look over there.

351
00:30:11,890 --> 00:30:12,590
Don't be afraid.

352
00:30:13,690 --> 00:30:14,410
Don't be afraid.

353
00:30:17,060 --> 00:30:18,100
Keep looking.

354
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:30,270
Mr. He, please save him.

355
00:30:30,290 --> 00:30:31,090
He's not a bad guy.

356
00:30:31,120 --> 00:30:31,840
No.

357
00:30:31,860 --> 00:30:33,470
I know he's not a bad guy.

358
00:30:33,500 --> 00:30:34,710
But the only person who can help him

359
00:30:34,740 --> 00:30:35,940
is you, Cong.

360
00:30:38,510 --> 00:30:39,710
You're the Lord's child.

361
00:30:39,930 --> 00:30:41,870
All the envoys answer to you.

362
00:30:43,410 --> 00:30:44,480
Only you can save him.

363
00:30:44,500 --> 00:30:46,630
Only after you wake up can you help him.

364
00:30:50,550 --> 00:30:50,990
No.

365
00:30:51,420 --> 00:30:52,460
I don't want to wake up.

366
00:30:56,170 --> 00:30:56,810
Don't be afraid.

367
00:30:58,910 --> 00:30:59,720
Don't be afraid.

368
00:31:41,910 --> 00:31:42,630
Cong.

369
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:44,870
You need to hurry up.

370
00:31:45,050 --> 00:31:45,800
What should I do?

371
00:31:45,940 --> 00:31:47,420
Cong. Cong.

372
00:31:48,770 --> 00:31:49,900
Close your eyes.

373
00:31:50,630 --> 00:31:51,500
Feel him with your heart.

374
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:52,160
Close your eyes.

375
00:31:53,550 --> 00:31:54,260
Yes.

376
00:31:56,550 --> 00:31:57,310
Yes.

377
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:05,520
Cong, don't resist the Lord's will.

378
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,350
Accept it.

379
00:32:09,130 --> 00:32:10,730
That monster is just your disciple.

380
00:32:10,760 --> 00:32:12,030
You can control it.

381
00:33:41,410 --> 00:33:42,050
You made it.

382
00:33:44,040 --> 00:33:44,760
You made it.

383
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:50,850
The great cause is about to succeed!

384
00:33:57,340 --> 00:33:58,140
Take a bite.

385
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:50,270
When did it happen?

386
00:34:50,949 --> 00:34:51,900
Two hours ago.

387
00:34:55,909 --> 00:34:56,739
How did it happen?

388
00:34:57,980 --> 00:34:59,470
The medic wanted to check the cells,

389
00:34:59,800 --> 00:35:01,000
so I let him in.

390
00:35:01,350 --> 00:35:02,260
Not long after,

391
00:35:02,290 --> 00:35:03,330
I heard screaming.

392
00:35:03,950 --> 00:35:04,830
When I found him,

393
00:35:05,390 --> 00:35:06,310
he was already dead.

394
00:35:09,110 --> 00:35:10,120
Was there anyone else

395
00:35:10,390 --> 00:35:11,470
