396
00:35:11,870 --> 00:35:12,710
No.

397
00:35:12,970 --> 00:35:13,970
Only the medic was there.

398
00:35:16,910 --> 00:35:17,610
Bring some men.

399
00:35:17,680 --> 00:35:18,670
